               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Pōkar Nikaṇṭu</title>, that is, the "Thesaurus of Pōkar", a Siddha medical work by <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author" key="Pōkanātar">Pōkar</persName> alias <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author" key="Pōkanātar">Pōkanātar</persName>. See Zvelebil (1995, p. 566, s.v. Pōkar). Abbreviated version (<foreign xml:lang="ta">curukkam</foreign>) in the form of a dictionary (<foreign xml:lang="ta">akarāti</foreign>), Tamil-Tamil. Each entry receives a definition, followed by a number between parentheses.</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (March 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>      </summary>
                  
